ronounced ‘bee-<b>veen</b>’). The actress  Vivien Leigh  (  1913–67 ) was christened <i>Vivian</i>."]},{"name":"Vivian","meanings":["Originally a boy's name, from an Old French form of the Latin name <i>Vivianus</i> (probably a derivative of <i>vivus</i> ‘alive’), but now more frequent as a girl's name. The name was borne by a 5th-century bishop of Saintes in western France, remembered for protecting his people during the invasion of the Visigoths."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Gace IV de Poissy was born about 1110 as the son of Gasce III de Poissy. He had at least 4 sons with Mabilie. He died in 1172, at the age of 63."},"et":{"ABT 1110–1172":"umbes 1110–1172","1110–1172":"1110–1172","–Female":"Surnud","1140–1189":"1140–1189","–1160":"–1160","–1147":"–1147","ABT 1140":"umbes 1140","ABT 1110":"umbes 1110","1147":"1147","from 1141 to 1147":"1141 kuni 1147","after 1160":"pärast 1160","1189":"1189","1110":"1110","1140":"1140","1172":"1172","1160":"1160"},"fi":{"ABT 1110–1172":"noin 1110–1172","1110–1172":"1110–1172","–Female":"Kuollut","1140–1189":"1140–1189","–1160":"–1160","–1147":"–1147","ABT 1140":"noin 1140","ABT 1110":"noin 1110","1147":"1147","from 1141 to 1147":"vuodesta 1141 vuoteen 1147","after 1160":"1160 jälkeen","1189":"1189","1110":"1110","1140":"1140","1172":"1172","1160":"1160"},"fr":{"ABT 1110–1172":"environ 1110–1172","1110–1172":"1110–1172","–Female":"Décédée","1140–1189":"1140–1189","–1160":"–1160","–1147":"–1147","ABT 1140":"environ 1140","ABT 1110":"environ 1110","1147":"1147","from 1141 to 1147":"du 1141 au 1147","after 1160":"après 1160","1189":"1189","1110":"1110","1140":"1140","1172":"1172","1160":"1160","lifeSummary":"Gace IV de Poissy est né environ 1110, fils de Gasce III de Poissy. Il a eu au moins 4 fils avec Mabilie. Il est décédé en 1172, à l’âge de 63 ans."},"de":{"ABT 1110–1172":"um 1110–1172","1110–1172":"1110–1172","–Female":"Verstorben","1140–1189":"1140–1189","–1160":"–1160","–1147":"–1147","ABT 1140":"um 1140","ABT 1110":"um 1110","1147":